# --- 1. 全域資料庫與系統日誌 ---
pgdata/
*.log
.env

# --- 2. 後端：遞迴排除所有編譯與暫存目錄 ---
**/bin/
**/build/
**/target/
**/out/
**/.gradle/
**/*.class
**/*.jar
# 允許追蹤 gradle-wrapper.jar，解決雲端部署找不到引導程式的問題
!**/gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar

# --- 3. 前端：遞迴排除依賴與打包物 ---
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
**/*.local

# --- 4. IDE 開發工具配置 (允許擴充設定) ---
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr
.vscode/
!.vscode/extensions.json
.DS_Store

# --- 5. 隱私與敏感檔案 ---
docs/raw/
*.pem
*.key
*.secret
*.jks
